Sample Game
This is the game that is written in C++. In this project, I am writting a program that similate a game. User will be able to

- Level Up via battle (in progress)
* Currently develop a new level system: setting up that the level system will not depend on .txt file but will be handle by if-else statement
* Adding one more feature in player class: exp to keep track of levels
* Obtaining money from battle. User will be able to use the money to buy equipments

- Save your information (completed)
- Load your infornation (completed)

Future design:
- able to purchase items
- adding a new feature: avoid rate
- cheating code such as increaase attack point, decrease monster's attack...etc 
